summary: An ordinance providing for the rezoning of Lots 1, 2, 3 and 4, Turner's Supplemental Plat of the east 1/2 of Block 52, D. S. Maynard's Addition, located on the northwest corner of Dearborn Street and 8th Avenue South; and Lots 10 to 21 inclusive, Block 2, Fauntleroy View Addition, located on the west side of 42nd Avenue Southwest, between West Thistle Street and West Cloverdale Street, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-9 and 17-8 respectively.
